# PSP Service Project Rules

## Language Requirement

**ALL content MUST be written in English**

This applies to:
- All documentation files
- All code comments
- All API documentation
- All README files
- All technical specifications
- All configuration files
- All database schemas
- All migration scripts
- All test files
- All user guides
- All error messages
- All variable names
- All function names
- All class names

**No exceptions. Everything must be in English.**
